{"tid":891224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國人竟無權知道中國國土的版圖？","createTime":"2018-11-06T02:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T02:22:29.000Z","uid":72963,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b699327dd4dad5135a249f55a355149032c443bf","tid":891224,"uid":72963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T02:09:33.000Z","msg":"中國人竟無權知道中國國土的版圖？沒錯！中國的北京高院周一（5日）宣佈這個消息。 <br />\n<br />\n事情起源於，去年8月15日，中國市民殷敏鴻中國向外交部申請政府訊息公開，質問「1949年以後（中俄建交後），中華人民共和國政府有沒有簽署過放棄中國國土（唐努烏梁海地區，Tannu Uriankhai）的協議？」 <br />\n<br />\n中國外交部在一個月後終於回函，但聲稱「根據《中華人民共和政府訊息公開條例》第14條和第21條，你申請的訊息涉密，不屬於政府訊息公開範疇。」回函還指，如不服答覆，可申請行政覆議，或向北京市第三中級人民法院提起行政訴訟。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181106/640_08f03ca034f0aee203e9a4429252d391.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181106%2F640_08f03ca034f0aee203e9a4429252d391.jpg&h=452f5919&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181106/640_29181941e635ec88742aa05d15b6a015.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181106%2F640_29181941e635ec88742aa05d15b6a015.jpg&h=2ffb94f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n殷敏鴻真的「乖乖聽話」，於今年3月7日，向北京市第三中級人民法院起訴中國外交部。不過，法院決定不受理，殷敏鴻鐵了心「問到底」，又就「法院不受理」上訴，要求予以立案，但仍被駁回。 <br />\n<br />\n消息曝光後，中國的律酷法律服務有限公司忍不住透過微信感慨：「這麼簡單問題，為什麼搞的這麼複雜」，並推測：「1. 據（中國）外交部答覆，顯示中國領土版圖涉密，中國人沒有權利知道。2.據北京高院回答，顯示外交部答覆正確，我們（高院）不管。中國的版圖中國人不能知道」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181106/640_e32139f4cbd45d0fd0cb15f5128af626.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181106%2F640_e32139f4cbd45d0fd0cb15f5128af626.jpg&h=ef8272a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此外，「律酷法律」還提醒殷敏鴻，據中國刑法第282條指出，非法獲取國家秘密的人，可處3年以下有期徒刑、拘役、管制或者剝奪政治權利；情節嚴重的，處3年以上7年以下有期徒刑。若中國人知道中國實際版圖，可能會被追究刑事責任。 <br />\n<br />\n唐努烏梁海原屬於中國的領土，1914年被俄羅斯帝國（沙俄）佔領16.8604萬平方公里，現由俄羅斯圖瓦共和國管理。 <br />\n<br />\n（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"be07f0f080bc28f7595d301f460e1a11442da9cc","tid":891224,"uid":72963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T02:11:28.000Z","msg":"支那人交稅就有份,,,   其他野多問就非法獲取國家秘密<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e067c06dd5c510f7eaa4ae371d9133e1d2bcf8fe","tid":891224,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T02:15:10.000Z","msg":"自古以來就是國家機密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6753c56f28ef03db6e852e17890837231164df17","tid":891224,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T02:16:02.000Z","msg":"又一個無五毛既post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3081f7f7d3b2d3f938c36bd650d8a86a11818606","tid":891224,"uid":72963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T02:16:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181106/1460991/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181106%2F1460991%2F&d=%2FDbU59RiNU1FRFg6cnXZppZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=50d636fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181106%2F1460991%2F&h=c6e9d202\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181106/1460991/</a><br />\n補返source"},{"pid":"e7dada70e4a3a4a4754189a2c1a6b6927d56cdc2","tid":891224,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T02:18:44.000Z","msg":"中國國土擁有人係中共，平民無權知道其它人同其它組織既資產"},{"pid":"76b1912f1132b44d2319da599105301ba38da498","tid":891224,"uid":36142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T02:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5acd9cfbdcdf92b35ee7191d373e8db903933f09","tid":891224,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T02:22:29.000Z","msg":"殘體慎入<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uFL1ras.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuFL1ras.png&h=1c711704&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}